      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; SST k-omega turbulence model selection justified by prior literature.",
      "rationale": "Formal model form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2. The SST k-omega model is the consensus choice for centrifugal pump hemolysis CFD per published benchmarking studies. No contraindications to the model form have been reported in the literature consulted."
    },
    {
